{"tid":634414,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人好後悔曾經入場支持DC電影？","createTime":"2018-04-19T08:08:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-12T05:47:25.000Z","uid":86587,"like":97,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"9d920ba4465e77946653dc360fd5f8c9d0e7e487","tid":634414,"uid":86587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T08:08:57.000Z","msg":"Man of steel打後無一套好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，套戲我見有路蘭個名諗住入場支持吓，點知前半段悶到仆場，係咁慢鏡頭整啲聖經隱喻懶係有深度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 後半段就係咁打打到完場，睇到想嘔，個體驗仲衰過睇變形金剛4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 舊版超人完全無懶係深度，反而成為一代經典，DC你地好好檢討吓諗吓點解喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後嗰幾套有多爛相信大家都知道，唔洗我多講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 特別要提嘅係wonder woman，套戲嚴重比人高估，個故事同道理好平平無奇，真實水平只係同deadpool差唔多，評分咁高只係女權因素<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> DC撚就係咁拎套wonder woman打飛機，真係可悲，你見有marvel撚拎套黑豹打飛機話好有深度咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講真，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>想DC好，最好嘅方法就係唔好入場為爛片貢獻票房</strong></span>， 如果啲高層見到亂拍都有人睇，就唔會比心機改善DC架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7107388e411ac824122d285a5d43f12d715bad6c","tid":634414,"uid":127494,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T08:10:30.000Z","msg":"好地地一套JL比人cut 走成個鐘...仲可以講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c83736a5e53948dcf8f70973c8d11355d1542827","tid":634414,"uid":52459,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T08:11:56.000Z","msg":"當做善事囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40a560cfdcf60747ddff27418ab3b3cebc052c6b","tid":634414,"uid":11143,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,