>\n<br />\n到WW, 唯一一套冇屌住走既, 但都只係合格<br />\n<br />\n到JL, 睇完已經同自己講真係最後一次入場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總結, DC完全浪費好題材, 好角色, 好演員, 好導演, 留番錢2刷復仇者3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28e3d5147a6119cb80fbc8dfd542b99c9159da52","tid":634414,"uid":48791,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T09:44:50.000Z","msg":"後悔曾經做隻dceu狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ae18a7ec49a0f0d049212e8ed163ec7c960d4c9","tid":634414,"uid":86587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T02:44:41.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbfb4a9462832390222428f8f199a3908b2a3a6f","tid":634414,"uid":180402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T02:50:33.000Z","msg":"有<br />\njustice league 同suicide squad <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nd劇情感覺上好薄弱 <br />\nww同好少少 但其實都係去睇gal<br />\n以後都唔想比錢dc"},{"pid":"df9009d11b69a3021971e0e376dbd29149ab498b","tid":634414,"uid":159798,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T02:51:57.000Z","msg":"BVS好正喎，真係有popcorn加少許深度<br />\nWW平平無奇，SS JL係垃圾<br />\n電影宇宙鋪排都係垃圾"},{"pid":"02a279407e4cd5bfcf19583909a46084f551c9e8","tid":634414,"uid":96964,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T02:56:55.000Z","msg":"JL個票房已經令到DC Entertainment 班高層比人炒晒"},{"pid":"1b9cdda55bed2069798a8703289462de433f8a41","tid":634414,"uid":179378,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T03:08:49.000Z","msg":"Mos我會畀8分，bvs 4分，ss 3分<br />\n其他冇睇了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdb521f5e23bec203bc91889f892a76ce2ad7a57","tid":634414,"uid":86587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote"